    "title_zh": "创意策划总监 | 媒体人 | 故事讲述与IP构建",
    "bio_en": "With over a decade of front-line media and large-scale event experience, I am a cross-disciplinary creative professional who serves as a large-scale event director, project manager, journalist, and editor. Specializing in Storytelling and IP development, I excel at transforming creative concepts into executable online and on-site experiences by integrating media, art, and technology to craft immersive, emotionally resonant experiences. I also bring extensive connections with professionals and institutions in the arts, culture, and media sectors both domestically and internationally, along with comprehensive capabilities spanning from creative strategy to full-scale project execution.",
    "bio_zh": "拥有十余年一线媒体与大型活动工作经验，集大型活动导演、项目经理、记者、编导、于一身的跨领域创意策划者。擅长以叙事和IP构造为核心，将创意概念转化为可落地的现场体验，融合媒体、艺术与科技，打造沉浸式、有情感共鸣的线上和现场体验。拥有丰富的海内外艺术、文化、媒介领域专业人士与机构资源，具备从创意策划到全案落地的综合能力。",
    "quote_en": "Good ideas don’t come from nowhere—they come from extensive research and groundwork, a sound way of thinking, rich industry experience, certain techniques and methods, a keen sense of generational shifts, breadth of mind, aesthetic judgment, the habit of jotting things down anytime, anywhere... and, ultimately, a moment of grace.",
    "quote_zh": "好的创意并非凭空而来，而是来自：大量的资料收集与案头工作，一个好的思维方式，丰富的行业经验，一些技巧与方法，对“代际”的敏锐感知，思维的宽阔性，审美判断力，随时随地记录的习惯，……还有，一个天赋的时刻。",
    "education_en": "Interactive Media Arts (MA), Tisch School of the Arts, New York University\nMember of Shanghai New Art Workers Association (NAWA)",
    "education_zh": "纽约大学 蒂施艺术学院 交互媒体艺术硕士\n上海新文艺工作者联合会 会员",
