          "id": "resonance",
          "title_en": "Interactive Art Installation: The Starfield of Resonance",
          "title_zh": "交互艺术装置《共鸣星域》",
          "cover": "/images/home/14.jpg",
          "imageFolder": "resonance",
          "content_zh": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "【入选上海Future Lab 2025展览和获邀迪拜Prototype for Humanity2026参展】"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "情感化实时交互艺术装置：通过计算机视觉识别用户表情，触发实时生成的视听内容反馈，构建一个“情感感知—内容生成”的闭环交互系统。该项目是一个探索艺术体验个性化与情绪响应式叙事的技术原型，打造具有情感深度的沉浸式艺术装置或展览互动环节。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "1.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "link",
              "text": "相关链接",
              "url": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1eC3QtkNbqGQim_PPsh-YOO33SevPLEcl/view?usp=sharing"
            }
          ],
          "content_en": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "[Selected for Future Lab 2025 Exhibition in Shanghai and Invited to Exhibit at Prototype for Humanity 2026 in Dubai]"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "An AI-driven project where two participants each control a drifting star on screen.\nWhen they smile together, their stars resonate — triggering a burst of glowing particles and sound.\nThe experience fosters positive human connection and reminds us to cherish the small, yet meaningful, moments of encounter."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "1.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "link",
              "text": "Related Link",
              "url": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1eC3QtkNbqGQim_PPsh-YOO33SevPLEcl/view?usp=sharing"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "night-ode",
          "title_en": "Interactive Art Installation: Ode to the Night",
          "title_zh": "交互艺术装置《夜的颂歌》",
          "cover": "/images/home/8.jpg",
          "imageFolder": "night-ode",
          "content_zh": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "沉浸式意境空间交互装置：通过将参与者物理动作实时映射为虚拟星空的位移，创造“星空随动”的沉浸体验。此装置作品将抽象意境转化为线下可感知、可互动的实体体验，展示了如何通过软硬件集成与交互设计，将叙事与情感在物理空间中具象化，适用于艺术展览、商业空间氛围打造等领域。作品在纽约进行了展览。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "1.jpg",
                "2.jpg",
                "3.jpg",
                "4.jpg",
                "5.jpg",
                "6.jpg",
                "7.jpg"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "content_en": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Inspired by the poet Haizi's line: \"The sky has nothing — why does it comfort me?\"\nThis project is created through both software and hardware programming.\nParticipants enter the installation space and put on interactive glasses; as they move, the stars above shimmer and follow the direction of their gaze. The work was exhibited in New York."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "1.jpg",
                "2.jpg",
                "3.jpg",
                "4.jpg",
                "5.jpg",
                "6.jpg",
                "7.jpg"
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
