        {
          "id": "nature",
          "title_en": "Art Installation: Under the Nature",
          "title_zh": "艺术装置《自然之下》",
          "cover": "/images/home/16.jpg",
          "imageFolder": "nature",
          "content_zh": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "人们不断向自然索取，表达着这样那样的欲望，同时也使得代表自然的大树变得不堪重负。我们渴望更好的生活，也需要意识到，这份生存所需，对自然而言，意味着怎样的负担。这正呼应了“公民生态”（Civic Ecologies）的主题——在发展与责任之间，重新思考我们与自然共生的方式。\n所以名字命名为《自然之下》。\n该项目在柏林展出。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "1.jpg",
                "2.jpg",
                "3.jpg",
                "4.jpg"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "content_en": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Humanity constantly takes from nature, expressing one desire after another, burdening the tree that represents nature until it can no longer bear the weight. This echoes the theme of \"Civic Ecologies\" — rethinking the way we coexist with nature.\nThus, the piece is titled Under the Nature.\nThe project was exhibited in Berlin."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "1.jpg",
                "2.jpg",
                "3.jpg",
                "4.jpg"
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
