        {
          "id": "instaknow",
          "title_en": "AI Video: Instaknow",
          "title_zh": "AI视频《Instaknow》",
          "cover": "/images/home/13.jpg",
          "imageFolder": "instaknow",
          "content_zh": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "多模态AIGC短视频生成管线：综合运用Suno（音乐生成）、PixVerse（视频生成）等各类音视频生成模型，完成从文本剧本到动态成片的端到端科幻短片创作。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "1.jpg",
                "2.jpg",
                "3.jpg",
                "4.jpg",
                "5.jpg",
                "6.jpg"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "content_en": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Multimodal AIGC Short Video Generation Pipeline: A comprehensive application of various audio and video generation models including Suno and PixVerse to complete an end-to-end science fiction short film creation."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "1.jpg",
                "2.jpg",
                "3.jpg",
                "4.jpg",
                "5.jpg",
                "6.jpg"
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "50days",
          "title_en": "AI Visual Design: 50 Days of Making",
          "title_zh": "AI视觉设计《重构五十日》",
          "cover": "/images/home/21.jpg",
          "imageFolder": "50days",
          "content_zh": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "连续50天，使用AI绘图工具，以全新的视角去创作戏剧和影视中的经典人物造型。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "1.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "索尔的新工作：一名维修高压线的电工。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "2.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "隆重介绍「浩克搬家公司」——世界上最适合帮你搬家的人。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "3.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "抵达迅速、定位精准，自带保温和加热系统，食物恒温，还能变形装载任何尺寸的货物。钢铁侠简直是为送外卖而生的。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "4.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "蝙蝠侠再就业——魔术师。表演魔术，变出一只活鸽子。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "5.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "蜘蛛侠，在互联网上织网。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "6.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "在蒂芙尼吃晚餐？"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "7.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "肯，一个精致、热爱时尚的男孩。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "8.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "一个是街头涂鸦风，另一个是脏脏的工业朋克风。\n「不是你的玩偶！」——芭比"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "9.jpg",
                "10.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "作品灵感来自马克·罗斯科的风格，面具来自中国傩戏。红色代表忠诚。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "11.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "魅影的灵感来自中国传统水墨画。源于《歌剧魅影》，黑白与阴阳的概念映照出他性格中的矛盾。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "12.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "《指环王》中加拉德瑞尔的自然之灵版本。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "13.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "两个人为了赢得奖金，四处寻找一只鸽子。\n他们能找多久？一年、十年、二十年，还是五十年？\n《东四十条》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "14.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "一个机甲艺伎。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "15.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "一个向来可靠，另一个同样可靠——只是你可能需要花点时间才能发现。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "16.jpg",
                "17.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "弗雷德和乔治·韦斯莱，与贝拉特里克斯·莱斯特兰奇。他们都拥有从未经历过内心冲突的性格。区别在于，双子创造并分享快乐，而贝拉特里克斯以毁灭为乐。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "18.jpg",
                "19.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "卢娜和小天狼星——行走于光影之中最明亮、最动人的灵魂。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "20.jpg",
                "21.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "「你选错了路，汤姆。你永远不会懂得爱。」\n邓布利多与伏地魔，黑与白的对比。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "22.jpg",
                "23.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "中国皮影戏风格的《哈利·波特》。皮影戏和电影一样，都是「光影」的艺术。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "24.jpg",
                "25.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "「平衡就是物理学，重心——」\n「我更愿意相信它是关于相信自己……还有独角兽。」\n《老友记》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "26.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "「如果我死了，你也死了，咱俩都死了……谁来打扫公寓啊？」\n《老友记》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "27.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "乔伊·崔比亚尼的天堂\n《老友记》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "28.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "创业基金总额：4.11 美元\n《破产姐妹》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "29.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "「我在做巧克力，当然。但不是普通的巧克力——我在做梦想。」\n《旺卡》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "30.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "「待在这儿。我去拿那棵植物。」\n《机器人总动员》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "31.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "「你知道吗？贫穷里没有什么高尚。」\n《华尔街之狼》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "32.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "「你这种人一抓一大把！」\n《推销员之死》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "33.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "灵感来自《吸血鬼日记》，黑色裙子上布满血一般的红色纹路。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "34.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "摇滚版孙悟空，以中国传统剪纸风格呈现。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "35.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "一幅中国水墨画风格的艾莎肖像，融合水彩质感与冰雪元素。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "36.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "花木兰——中国北魏时期的传奇女战士。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "37.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "在格林兄弟的《灰姑娘》中，鸟儿为女主角带来金色裙子和金鞋。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "38.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "《白雪公主》的历史原型可能源于18世纪的德国。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "39.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "2025年版的程蝶衣，灵感来自《霸王别姬》。如果生在更晚的时代，他能否挣脱悲剧的命运？"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "40.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "行星海盗版美少女战士"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "41.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "秦彻——《恋与深空》中的核心角色。"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "42.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "《孔雀》——一个美丽的男孩，用自己孤独的方式守护着心爱的女孩。\n《剪刀手爱德华》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "43.jpg",
                "44.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "青蛇\n《白蛇传》"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "45.jpg"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "content_en": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "50 consecutive days of using AI drawing tools to reimagine classic character designs from theater, film, and television from a fresh perspective."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "1.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Thor's new job: an electrician repairing high-voltage power lines."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "2.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Introducing Hulk Moving Express — the most qualified man in the world to help you move."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "3.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Speedy arrival, precise positioning, equipped with insulation and heating system. Iron Man was practically born to deliver takeout."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "4.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Batman re-employment — magician. Performing a magic trick, pulling out a live pigeon."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "5.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Spider-Man weaving his web on the internet."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "6.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Dinner at Tiffany's?"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "7.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Ken, a refined and fashion-loving boy."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "8.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "One is the street graffiti style, and the other is the dirty industrial punk style.\n\"Not your doll!\" — by Barbie"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "9.jpg",
                "10.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Inspired by Mark Rothko. The face masks are from Chinese Nuo opera. Red represents loyalty."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "11.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The Phantom is inspired by traditional Chinese ink painting. From The Phantom of the Opera."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "12.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The nature spirit version of Galadriel, from The Lord of the Rings."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "13.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Two people searching for a pigeon in hopes of winning a prize.\nHow long can they keep searching? One year, ten years, twenty, or fifty?\nDance Still"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "14.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "It's a mech-geisha."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "15.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "One who has always been reliable, and another who is just as reliable."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "16.jpg",
                "17.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Fred and George Weasley, and Bellatrix Lestrange. The twins create and share joy; Bellatrix finds pleasure in destruction."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "18.jpg",
                "19.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Luna and Sirius — among the most luminous souls to walk in shadow and light."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "20.jpg",
                "21.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Dumbledore and Voldemort, the contrast between black and white."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "22.jpg",
                "23.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Harry Potter in the style of Chinese shadow puppetry. Shadow play, like cinema, is an art of light and shadow."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "24.jpg",
                "25.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"Balance is all about physics, center of gravity—\"\n\"I prefer to think it's about believing in yourself… and unicorns.\"\nFriends"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "26.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"If I die, and you die, and we're both dead... who's gonna clean the apartment?\"\nFriends"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "27.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Joey Tribbiani's Paradise\nFriends"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "28.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Total Entrepreneurial Fund: $4.11\n2 Broke Girls"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "29.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"I'm making chocolate, of course. But not just any chocolate—I'm making dreams.\"\nWonka"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "30.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"Stay here. I'll get the plant.\"\nWALL-E"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "31.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"There's no nobility in poverty.\"\nThe Wolf of Wall Street"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "32.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"You're a dime a dozen!\"\nDeath of a Salesman"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "33.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Inspired by The Vampire Diaries, with a black dress veined with red like blood."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "34.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A rock and roll version of Monkey King in traditional Chinese paper-cutting style."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "35.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A Chinese ink painting portrait of Elsa, blending watercolor textures with icy elements."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "36.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Mulan — A legendary female warrior of the Northern Wei Dynasty."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "37.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In the Grimm brothers' Cinderella, birds bring a dazzling golden dress and real golden shoes."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "38.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The historical prototype of Snow White may have originated in 18th-century Germany."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "39.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "2025 version of Cheng Dieyi, inspired by Farewell My Concubine."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "40.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Planet Pirate Version of Sailor Moon"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "41.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Sylus — from Love and Deepspace."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "42.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The Peacock / Edward Scissorhands — guarding the girl he loves in his own lonely way."
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "43.jpg",
                "44.jpg"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Green Snake / The Legend of the White Snake"
            },
            {
              "type": "images",
              "files": [
                "45.jpg"
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}